Thanks to Dominique Rousset of the Laboratoire de Geophysique
Universite de Pau et des Pays de l'Adour  for permission
to include the seg2segy programs written by Brett Bennett.


Utility program to convert SEG2 file in SEGY format.

The following files are included in this directory:

- README : this file

- seg2segyBE.c : ANSI C source file big endian machines
- seg2segyLE.c : ANSI C source file for little endian machines

- segykeyw.ord : text file used at execution. Up to now, it should be present
in the same directory as the file to convert.

compilation :
  no extra library nor include file needed. use standard compilation command
  for instance : cc -O -oseg2segy seg2segyBE.c
  
  
  
  credit : Brett Bennett 
  A computer program to convert SEG-2 data to SEG-Y 
  Special report Geophysics #55 Sept. 1990 pp 1272-1284
  

